<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:ttp="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#parameter" xmlns:composer="https://composer.boidu.dev/ttml" ttp:timeBase="media" xml:lang="en" composer:timing="Line"><head><metadata><ttm:title>tommy. - eat your heart (feat. Hatsune Miku)</ttm:title><ttm:agent xml:id="v1" type="person"><ttm:name>tommy.</ttm:name></ttm:agent><ttm:agent xml:id="v2" type="person"><ttm:name>Hatsune Miku</ttm:name></ttm:agent><ttm:agent xml:id="v3" type="group"><ttm:name>tommy. &amp; Hatsune Miku</ttm:name></ttm:agent></metadata></head><body dur="2:51.737"><div><p begin="0:00.099" end="0:03.016" ttm:agent="v2">(And would you break your bones for me, don't lie)</p><p begin="0:03.085" end="0:06.784" ttm:agent="v2">(And would you eat your heart for me tonight)</p><p begin="0:06.794" end="0:10.303" ttm:agent="v2">(And would you break your bones for me, don't lie)</p><p begin="0:10.460" end="0:14.382" ttm:agent="v2">(And would you eat your heart for me tonight)</p><p begin="0:29.636" end="0:32.618" ttm:agent="v1">How do you know, what's good for me?</p><p begin="0:32.618" end="0:36.235" ttm:agent="v1">I could be who I want, if you just let me breathe</p><p begin="0:36.235" end="0:38.592" ttm:agent="v1">I need you out of my way</p><p begin="0:38.592" end="0:39.981" ttm:agent="v1">Or on your knees</p><p begin="0:39.981" end="0:41.904" ttm:agent="v2">No, you don't pray to god</p><p begin="0:41.904" end="0:43.901" ttm:agent="v2">Baby, you pray to me</p><p begin="0:43.901" end="0:46.274" ttm:agent="v2">If the door is locked but it says vacant</p><p begin="0:46.274" end="0:47.540" ttm:agent="v2">Know that you ain't safe</p><p begin="0:47.540" end="0:49.471" ttm:agent="v2">You can run right down the hallway</p><p begin="0:49.471" end="0:51.200" ttm:agent="v2">Now you know I love a chase</p><p begin="0:51.449" end="0:53.098" ttm:agent="v1">Crawling inside of your body</p><p begin="0:53.098" end="0:55.083" ttm:agent="v2">Grippin' your heart like a hobby</p><p begin="0:55.083" end="0:58.729" ttm:agent="v3">But you wanna know, what i think?</p><p begin="0:59.206" end="1:02.631" ttm:agent="v1">I don't see you how I used to</p><p begin="1:02.631" end="1:06.303" ttm:agent="v2">But I can feel your touch is there</p><p begin="1:06.303" end="1:09.994" ttm:agent="v1">There's something that I want to ask you</p><p begin="1:09.994" end="1:13.665" ttm:agent="v3">Was it really me, coming apart at the seams?</p><p begin="1:14.000" end="1:17.433" ttm:agent="v1">I don't see you how I used to</p><p begin="1:17.433" end="1:21.128" ttm:agent="v2">But I can feel your touch is there</p><p begin="1:21.128" end="1:24.863" ttm:agent="v1">There's something that i want to ask you</p><p begin="1:24.863" end="1:28.401" ttm:agent="v3">Was it really me, coming apart at the seams?</p><p begin="1:30.510" end="1:31.998" ttm:agent="v1">I wash you in the blood</p><p begin="1:31.998" end="1:33.820" ttm:agent="v1">I'm feeling some kind of rush</p><p begin="1:33.820" end="1:35.611" ttm:agent="v1">I'm burring up at your touch</p><p begin="1:35.611" end="1:37.138" ttm:agent="v1">You’re holding me and it’s—</p><p begin="1:37.810" end="1:39.423" ttm:agent="v1">I'm weeping in your arms</p><p begin="1:39.423" end="1:41.219" ttm:agent="v1">I'm screaming with no response</p><p begin="1:41.219" end="1:43.028" ttm:agent="v1">You give me nothing I want</p><p begin="1:43.028" end="1:44.626" ttm:agent="v1">But you whisper to me</p><p begin="1:44.626" end="1:48.278" ttm:agent="v2">And would you break your bones for me, don't lie?</p><p begin="1:48.278" end="1:52.086" ttm:agent="v2">And would you eat your heart for me tonight?</p><p begin="1:52.086" end="1:55.690" ttm:agent="v2">And would you break your bones for me, don't lie?</p><p begin="1:55.690" end="1:59.714" ttm:agent="v2">And would you eat your heart for me tonight?</p><p begin="2:00.184" end="2:03.525" ttm:agent="v1">I don't see you how I used to</p><p begin="2:03.525" end="2:07.313" ttm:agent="v2">But I can feel your touch is there</p><p begin="2:07.313" end="2:10.914" ttm:agent="v1">There's something that I want to ask you</p><p begin="2:10.914" end="2:14.870" ttm:agent="v3">Was it really me, coming apart at the seams?</p><p begin="2:14.870" end="2:18.272" ttm:agent="v1">I don't see you how I used to</p><p begin="2:18.272" end="2:21.928" ttm:agent="v2">But I can feel your touch is there</p><p begin="2:21.928" end="2:25.673" ttm:agent="v1">There's something that I want to ask you</p><p begin="2:25.673" end="2:28.978" ttm:agent="v3">Was it really me, coming apart at the seams?</p><p begin="2:28.978" end="2:32.556" ttm:agent="v1">(And would you break your bones for me, don't lie)</p><p begin="2:32.880" end="2:36.335" ttm:agent="v2">(And would you eat your heart for me tonight)</p><p begin="2:36.335" end="2:40.068" ttm:agent="v1">(And would you break your bones for me, don't lie)</p><p begin="2:40.873" end="2:44.180" ttm:agent="v2">(And would you eat your heart for me tonight)</p></div></body></tt>